text.tspan: • PCC Integration: Fetch patient EHR data
• Patient must have valid medical record
• EHR data must be current (≤7 days)
• Device Fitting: Schedule and configure NIV device
• Program Activation: Patient officially on NIV
• RT Visit Schedule: 7-day visit cycle begins
• Re-Review Scheduling: Set future assessment date
• Lab Orders: Generate required lab requests
• Blood Gas Orders: Schedule arterial blood gas
Business Rule: Qualified patients need consent
Business Rule: Check if more data needed
